            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h3 id=\"feature-genealogy-survival-vs-emergence\">Feature Genealogy: Survival vs. Emergence</h3>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">As we increase SAE width, do the same features persist or does the dictionary reorganize?\n<strong>Blue</strong> = features that existed at 16k and survived. <strong>Orange</strong> = newly emerged features.</span>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Only <strong>28-41%</strong> of 16k features survive to 1M \u2014 the dictionary fundamentally reorganizes.</span></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
      "console": []
    },
