          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h3 id=\"domain-specificity-emergence\">Domain-Specificity Emergence</h3>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Which refusal types do SAE features capture at each width?\n<strong>LPT</strong> is dominated by Safety/Legal (the \"should I refuse?\" signal).\n<strong>MRT</strong> shows a balanced mix \u2014 the \"how do I refuse?\" signal is domain-specific.</span></span>"
          }
        }
